column2: Alistair Rogers, Kim S. Ely and Shawn Serbin. 2017. Leaf Photosynthetic Parameters Vcmax and Jmax and Supporting Gas Exchange Data, Barrow, Alaska, 2012-2016. Next Generation Ecosystem Experiments Arctic Data Collection, Carbon Dioxide Information Analysis Center, Oak Ridge National Laboratory, Oak Ridge, Tennessee, USA. Accessed at http://dx.doi.org/10.5440/1336809

Measurement of leaf traits and gas exchange was conducted over an area of approximately 1 km2 centered at 71.28°N, 156.65°W. Raw gas exchange data used in Rogers et al 2017 to derive the photosynthetic parameters Vc,max and Jmax. The entry “-9999” represents data not available. Data collection as described by Rogers et al. (2017).
